got his ducks together.

31:57.166 --> 31:58.500
Don't be there.

31:58.834 --> 32:00.377
I can't anyway.

32:01.378 --> 32:03.505
I'm picking up a suspect
in an hour.

32:03.630 --> 32:05.341
Tomorrow's gonna be hard.

32:05.674 --> 32:07.092
Yeah. For both of us.

32:09.094 --> 32:10.596
Is there anything
you need to tell me?

32:11.597 --> 32:12.598
What?

32:12.931 --> 32:14.933
Look, I am your father.

32:15.017 --> 32:17.353
It's in my job description
to listen and help you
out if--

32:17.561 --> 32:20.189
Help with what?
I don't know, you tell me.

32:21.398 --> 32:23.233
Nothing to tell.

32:23.692 --> 32:25.736
Look, Deena, I'm not
here to lecture you

32:25.861 --> 32:28.781
or demand the truth
of whatever the hell
went down--

32:28.864 --> 32:30.199
Went down with what?

32:30.282 --> 32:31.909
I don't know.

32:32.034 --> 32:34.119
I'm just here
if you want to talk.

32:34.203 --> 32:36.705
Thank you. I don't.

32:39.458 --> 32:41.877
The next time we talk
may include a pane of glass

32:42.002 --> 32:43.837
and two telephones.

32:44.505 --> 32:46.673
So if there is anything...

32:47.383 --> 32:50.344
Dad, I got to go.

32:51.220 --> 32:52.554
Yeah.

32:53.555 --> 32:55.391
Yeah, I, uh,
I understand.

32:59.186 --> 33:00.854
Go do your job.

33:02.398 --> 33:04.191
Be careful.
Thank you.

33:06.443 --> 33:07.903
I love you.

33:15.077 --> 33:16.453
(SIGHS)

33:20.457 --> 33:22.584
WALKER: Okay, guys,
keep it simple in there.

33:22.668 --> 33:23.919
This is a high-risk warrant,

33:24.002 --> 33:26.338
so stay focused,
don't get bunched up.

33:26.422 --> 33:27.631
Are those both rolling?

33:27.756 --> 33:28.799
Yes.

33:28.924 --> 33:30.259
If shit goes south
in there,

33:30.384 --> 33:32.010
you give them
to me, okay?

33:32.594 --> 33:34.263
That wasn't the deal.

33:34.430 --> 33:35.639
Or you could give
them to him now,

33:35.764 --> 33:37.015
stay in the van.

33:38.475 --> 33:39.935
Okay.
Okay, good.

33:40.018 --> 33:41.562
Let's go. Good luck.

33:41.812 --> 33:44.648
(ACOUSTIC GUITAR PLAYING)

33:48.402 --> 33:49.695
(FOOTSTEPS)

33:51.613 --> 33:52.739
(CRASHING)

33:52.823 --> 33:53.907
Police!
(POLICEMEN SHOUTING)

33:53.991 --> 33:54.992
(SNARLING)

33:55.117 --> 33:56.452
Right here,
on your right!

33:56.577 --> 33:58.412
(GROWLING)
(GUNS COCKING)

34:00.706 --> 34:01.748
(SNARLING)

34:01.832 --> 34:02.916
Argh!

34:06.295 --> 34:07.796
(GROWLING)
Argh!

34:09.089 --> 34:10.716
POLICE 1: There he goes!
POLICE 2: Coming your way!

34:11.925 --> 34:12.926
Go, go!

34:13.469 --> 34:14.845
(DART GUN FIRES)

34:14.970 --> 34:16.305
(GROWLING)

34:16.638 --> 34:17.931
(SCREAMING)

34:18.557 --> 34:19.892
(DART GUN FIRES)

34:20.601 --> 34:21.852
(SNARLING)

34:21.977 --> 34:22.978
Hey!

34:24.480 --> 34:25.647
POLICE 1: He's down!

34:25.772 --> 34:26.857
Subject's down!

34:26.982 --> 34:28.025
POLICE 2: Secured.

34:28.317 --> 34:29.651
WALLACE: Not a match.

34:29.735 --> 34:31.320
If he bit the senator's
head off,

34:31.445 --> 34:33.322
it was with
a spitless mouth.

34:33.447 --> 34:34.656
No saliva.

34:34.781 --> 34:36.909
No matching DNA at all.

34:36.992 --> 34:39.411
No hair, no claw marks
on the exterior of the--

34:39.495 --> 34:40.621
Okay, enough.
Thank you.

34:40.704 --> 34:41.830
We get it.

34:41.955 --> 34:43.332
He alibi out?

34:43.457 --> 34:45.876
On the night in question,
he was at a bar in Bakersfield

34:46.001 --> 34:49.171
playing in a band
from 9:00 p.m.
till 4:00 in the morning.

34:50.714 --> 34:53.133
So, not your dog.

34:53.217 --> 34:54.843
No, only thing
he's guilty of

34:54.968 --> 34:58.555
is writing a stupid letter
to his ex-girlfriend.

34:59.473 --> 35:02.351
Speaking of letters,
we should get
to that hate mail.

35:02.434 --> 35:04.728
Uh, give me a minute.
I got a thing.

35:04.853 --> 35:06.480
Where you going?

35:06.563 --> 35:08.524
Her dad's trial,
I would think.

35:08.857 --> 35:10.234
That's today?

35:10.359 --> 35:11.652
(LAUGHS)
It's been all week.

35:11.735 --> 35:13.570
Shit. Ugh.

35:13.695 --> 35:15.948
But you've got a lot
on your mind, I guess.

35:19.535 --> 35:20.953
(SIGHS)

35:21.036 --> 35:22.663
(RINGING NOISE)
Argh!

35:24.998 --> 35:26.416
Mother...

35:35.968 --> 35:37.719
Holy shit, are you okay?

35:38.470 --> 35:39.721
Yeah.

35:40.055 --> 35:41.890
Yeah, terrific.

35:41.974 --> 35:43.267
What's up?

35:43.392 --> 35:44.393
(GROANING)

35:44.476 --> 35:45.727
Maybe now's
not a good time.

35:45.852 --> 35:47.229
Yeah, well,
haven't you noticed?

35:47.563 --> 35:49.856
Times are shitty
all over.

35:51.608 --> 35:53.569
Come, walk and talk.

35:53.652 --> 35:56.947
Okay, so Tiberio, Zora,
and I were thinking that--

35:57.072 --> 35:58.907
And who's...
who's Tiberio?

35:58.991 --> 36:00.492
That's Triphammer's
new recruit.

36:00.576 --> 36:02.619
Oh, yeah. Martinez.

36:02.744 --> 36:03.745
Yes.

36:04.496 --> 36:05.831
(SIGHS)

36:07.374 --> 36:08.792
You should go see a doctor.

36:10.752 --> 36:12.421
I did.

36:12.504 --> 36:15.340
He says
it's just a headache.

36:15.424 --> 36:17.801
I'm good.
What can I do for you?

36:18.927 --> 36:20.429
Well, we want to team up,

36:20.554 --> 36:21.680
but we need help.

36:21.805 --> 36:23.265
Help?

36:23.348 --> 36:24.558
Guidance.

36:25.934 --> 36:27.477
What kind of guidance?

36:27.603 --> 36:29.271
We want you to be
our Powers coach.

36:29.771 --> 36:31.273
(LAUGHING)

36:31.857 --> 36:33.275
Seriously?

36:33.567 --> 36:34.860
Come on, you've been there.

36:34.943 --> 36:36.069
Triphammer's gone,

36:36.153 --> 36:38.030
and who trained you?

36:38.280 --> 36:39.781
You didn't become
Diamond overnight.

36:39.865 --> 36:42.743
Somebody guided you,
like Janice or--

36:42.826 --> 36:44.119
It wasn't Janice.

36:45.037 --> 36:46.288
Who was it?

36:46.788 --> 36:48.248
Patrick.

36:48.665 --> 36:50.125
SuperShock.

36:50.500 --> 36:52.461
You're kidding me.
No.

36:52.628 --> 36:53.920
You should ask him.

36:54.004 --> 36:55.631
He'd probably get
a kick out of it.

36:55.881 --> 36:57.466
I'm asking you.

37:01.511 --> 37:05.057
Look, I appreciate it,

37:05.140 --> 37:08.143
and really,
it would be an honor.

37:08.226 --> 37:10.145
But...

37:10.270 --> 37:12.356
I'm not the right guy.

37:12.814 --> 37:13.982
You could be.

37:21.990 --> 37:24.493
I'm not, okay?
I'm sorry.

37:24.660 --> 37:25.994
I'm sorry.
Walker.

37:31.541 --> 37:33.835
God bless you. (LAUGHING)

37:33.919 --> 37:35.837
See you later.
You betcha.

37:37.047 --> 37:38.298
Ah.

37:38.715 --> 37:40.467
(LAUGHING)
What the fuck was that?

37:40.550 --> 37:42.719
That was the threat
of exposure.

37:42.844 --> 37:44.221
Certain people further up
the food chain

37:44.346 --> 37:45.847
weren't comfortable
with the idea

37:45.972 --> 37:49.434
of me being questioned,
and that ends that.

37:50.185 --> 37:53.355
Like I said,
the past is a bitch.

37:53.980 --> 37:55.857
(LAUGHS)
Yeah.

37:56.441 --> 37:57.943
So is the present.

37:58.360 --> 38:00.070
Doesn't have to be.

38:01.905 --> 38:03.573
So how do you do it?

38:04.366 --> 38:05.826
Do what?

38:06.118 --> 38:07.786
Get through every day,

38:07.869 --> 38:09.871
everyone thinking
you're a great cop,

38:09.955 --> 38:12.708
but you know in your heart
you're shit.

38:12.791 --> 38:14.710
No, Deena...
No, no, no, Dad.

38:14.793 --> 38:16.378
I really, um...

38:18.505 --> 38:19.965
I need to know.

38:23.427 --> 38:25.053
(SIGHS)

38:26.054 --> 38:27.514
You make allowances.

38:29.057 --> 38:30.726
Allowances?

38:30.809 --> 38:32.602
Yeah.
What?

38:32.728 --> 38:35.063
Like, you let things slide

38:35.147 --> 38:36.565
even though you know
you shouldn't,

38:36.690 --> 38:38.275
and that somehow
makes things better?

38:38.400 --> 38:39.568
Yes.

38:39.651 --> 38:42.696
The world needs this,
so you do that.

38:42.779 --> 38:44.114
Keep it simple.

38:44.239 --> 38:46.783
But you broke the law.

38:46.908 --> 38:49.077
You and your mother
deserved the best life
I could give you.

38:49.161 --> 38:51.037
You were my world.

38:51.580 --> 38:53.707
All I ever wanted to do,

38:53.790 --> 38:56.251
when I grew up
was be like you.

38:58.962 --> 39:00.380
Honey.

39:01.882 --> 39:03.800
Tell me what happened.

39:07.345 --> 39:08.764
I grew up.

39:11.683 --> 39:13.143
I grew up, Dad.

39:31.119 --> 39:32.537
(CELL PHONE RINGS)

39:41.379 --> 39:42.839
Hey.

39:43.298 --> 39:45.967
I'm sorry it didn't
work out for you.

39:46.468 --> 39:48.845
Oh, it worked out,
just not the way I'd hoped.

39:49.429 --> 39:50.806
How are you doing?

39:50.931 --> 39:52.140
I'm okay.

39:53.892 --> 39:55.227
I'm done for the day.
I was wondering

39:55.310 --> 39:56.812
if I could
buy you a--
No.

39:57.145 --> 39:58.772
You don't know what
I was going to say.

39:58.855 --> 40:00.982
Um, still, no.

40:01.942 --> 40:03.151
Okay.

40:03.276 --> 40:04.736
Rain check.

40:05.612 --> 40:08.031
Uh... yeah.

40:08.698 --> 40:10.242
Yeah.

40:11.743 --> 40:12.994
(BOMB WHISTLING)

40:13.662 --> 40:15.038
(LOUD EXPLOSION)

40:17.749 --> 40:19.835
MAN: (ON RADIO)
A few hours ago,
the world learned

40:19.960 --> 40:21.670
of the atomic bomb
and its use

40:21.795 --> 40:24.840
against the city of
Hiroshima in Japan.

40:24.923 --> 40:27.050
The descriptions
of this new weapon's

40:27.175 --> 40:30.387
devastating and awesome power
stagger the imagination.

40:33.598 --> 40:34.975
I'm sorry.

40:36.434 --> 40:37.602
I didn't know.

40:40.188 --> 40:42.399
If Truman's hand was forced,
then he had to.

40:42.732 --> 40:45.026
He did it.
He was there, too.

40:45.902 --> 40:47.404
Patrick, who was?

40:47.779 --> 40:49.030
As more information
comes to light,

40:49.155 --> 40:50.699
we await further developments

40:50.824 --> 40:51.908
from the White House
and President Truman...

40:52.033 --> 40:53.118
(CRUNCHING)

40:53.201 --> 40:54.911
Regarding the decision
to use this...

40:55.954 --> 40:57.664
He's a destroyer.

40:57.747 --> 40:59.332
He's everywhere.

40:59.416 --> 41:01.126
Who are you
talking about?

41:03.962 --> 41:05.380
The Ghost.

41:55.513 --> 41:57.724
PATRICK: I know
who killed him.

42:02.062 --> 42:03.939
Hey, Patrick, what are you--

42:04.064 --> 42:05.398
I know who killed
the Knight.

42:11.571 --> 42:12.989
Uh, who?

42:13.949 --> 42:15.158
It was him.

42:18.078 --> 42:19.412
Morrison.

42:19.537 --> 42:21.957
You might know him
better as The Ghost.

42:23.333 --> 42:26.086
He killed Senator Brown,
and...

42:26.503 --> 42:28.338
He's gonna kill me next.
